# Healthy Basket Groceries API

The Groceries API can be used to order groceries from the Healthy Basket store.
Items are things that can be purchased on the store via an Order. A Recipe can also contain Items needed to put that Recipe together.
There is also a list of Recalls that may contain Items and the associated period of each recall.

# Group Ordering APIs

## Item [/items/{ID}]
An item includes name, brand, amount, a description, price and the default quantity to be ordered.
There is also a link to an image.

+ Parameters

    + ID: "4" (string) - the item ID

### Retrieve Item [GET]
Retrieve a single item.

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)

        {
            "ID": "4",
            "name": "Brown Eggs",
            "brand": "Store",
            "amount": "1 dozen",
