# Group Recall APIs
        
## Recalls Collection [/recalls]
All recalls

### List all recalls [GET]
Recalls are an array, each with an ID, the relatedMinor  item ID and a start/end date in ISO8601 format.

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)

        [
            {
                "ID": "1",
                "itemID": "4",
                "start": "2017-09-07T20:00:00Z",
                "end": "2017-09-08T20:00:00Z"
            }
        ]